Others: GS Lakshmi is a cricketer who played for Andhra, Bihar, Railways, East Zone, and South Zone between 1989 and 2004.
She was selected for India's tour of England in 1999 but did not play a single match.
She was inducted to the ICC International Panel of Match Referees on 14th May 2019 and debuted as a match referee in a T20I match between Hong Kong vs Ireland played in Abu Dhabi (2019).
She officiated as a match referee in Men's ODI in UAE vs the United States, Sharjah (Dec 8, 2019).
She first officiated as the match referee in Domestic Women's Cricket in 2008-09.
